channel.title: 7 errors when adding Agility
channel.description:
agility.java:138: TeleTo(java.lang.String,int) in client cannot be applied to (int,int) p.TeleTo(X, Y); ^ agility.java:147: cannot find symbol symbol : variable ServerCP location: class agility p.playerSEW = ServerCP.walkemote; ^ client.java:1528: cannot find symbol symbol : variable agility location: class server server.agility.agility(objectID, playerId); ^ client.java:14997: cannot find symbol symbol : variable agility location: class server if(server.agility.agilityTimer > 0) ^ client.java:14998: cannot find symbol symbol : variable agility location: class server server.agility.agilityTimer--; ^ client.java:14999: cannot find symbol symbol : variable agility location: class server if(server.agility.agilityTimer == 1){ ^ client.java:15000: cannot find symbol symbol : variable agility location: class server server.agility.resetAgility(playerId); ^ Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 7 errors You have sucsessfully compiled Press any key to continue . . .
